scene_description_enriched: A crab, depicted in shades of orange and red, is shown in profile against a turquoise background, suggesting an aquatic environment. The crab has multiple legs and prominent claws. The scene is framed by a decorative, multi-lobed border with gold and black outlines, and further embellished with floral motifs and small insects in the margins. The overall presentation is within a stylized, quatrefoil-shaped compartment.
